These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, malaysian, indian, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, basketball, badminton, cycling
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, ship, scooter
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dannemann, siglo, pall-mall
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, may, april
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the malaysian##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the game-smoker is the turkish##1
 6. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the turkish##1
 8. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person driving the ship is the turkish##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality          | malaysian    | indian      | turkish  | russian     |
| Sport         | cycling    | badminton   | tennis | basketball      |
| Transport   | van       | jet-ski | ship     | scooter    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | dannemann         | game  | siglo    |
| Birthday           | may      | april       | november | july |

