.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: domino, bridge, poker, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, ship, jet-ski, helicopter
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, fuchsia, blood-red, ebony
There 4 different types of food: apricot, radish, pumpkin, potato
House: ranch-style, townhouse, art-deco, colonial
 1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 2. the person who likes grey is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 3. the colonial house is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the person eating radish is the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1
11. the person playing poker is on the left of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Game      | bridge      | domino     | poker    | backgammon |
| Transport   | tram | ship   | jet-ski   | helicopter           |
| Color   | fuchsia  | ebony     | blood-red    | grey         |
| Food           | potato         | radish | pumpkin     | apricot        |
| House         | ranch-style     | colonial  | townhouse | art-deco       |

