.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, tea, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, sports, romance, mystery
House: victorian, modern, townhouse, farmhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, sudoku, hiking, traveling
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, dahlia, lily
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who growslily is the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is the modern house##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the townhouse house##1
11. the person who growslily is on the left of the townhouse house##1
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Beverage          | lemonade    | iced-tea      | tea  | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | romance      | sports | family      |
| House           | modern       | victorian         | farmhouse  | townhouse         |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | sudoku | hiking  | traveling |
| Flower     | dahlia       | poppy         | lily   | daisy        |

