.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, soccer, rugby
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, reggae, jazz, folk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, azalea, begonia
City: hannover, london, berlin, rome
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, november, september
 1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left of the fan of pop##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Sport      | soccer   | rugby   | cricket      | climbing     |
| Music-Genre          | jazz     | pop   | folk | reggae |
| Flower   | iris | azalea | zinnia   | begonia       |
