 4. the person watching satire movies is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the colonial house is on the far right##1
 7. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is the ranch-style house##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is the person watching action movies##1
10. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
13. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
14. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

