.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, emerald, blood-red, green
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, sports, thriller, satire
House: cottage, craftsman, tower, modern
City: boston, marseilles, london, miami
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, backgammon, poker
 1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the cottage house##1
 2. the person watching family movies is the cottage house##1
 3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the modern house##1
 4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
 7. the modern house is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 9. the person who likes brown is the person playing billiard##1
10. the person who likes green is the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Color    | brown     | emerald  | green       | blood-red      |
| Movie-Genre       | thriller    | satire        | family  | sports      |
| House         | craftsman  | modern | cottage | tower |
| City         | boston | miami          | marseilles         | london      |
| Game   | billiard     | scrabble     | backgammon       | poker          |

