.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, metal, disco
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, prince, tiparillo, ritmeester
House: craftsman, cape-cod, palace, gothic-revival
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, brown, blood-red
City: prague, boston, paris, colone
 1. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of salsa is the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is the fan of metal##1
 6. the ritmeester-smoker is the fan of disco##1
 7. the prince-smoker is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is the palace house##1
10. the palace house is on the far left##1
11. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre      | disco       | metal      | salsa      | r&b    |
