 8. the owner of the horse is on the right of the police-officer##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the engineer##1
10. the owner of the horse is the entrepreneur##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the right of the videographer##1
12. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

