.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, light-blue, white, black
House: townhouse, cottage, craftsman, victorian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling, ice-hockey, soccer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, fanta, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, horror, disaster, romance
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is the townhouse house##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is the victorian house##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the right of the cottage house##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person who likes white is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person who likes black is the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Color        | light-blue    | black        | green        | white      |
| House       | craftsman       | townhouse       | cottage      | victorian |
| Sport         | cycling | soccer | ice-hockey | volleyball      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate          | coffee         | sprite           | fanta    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster         | horror       | romance     | superhero   |

 